      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "In illustration, cancer mortality rates are related to prevailing wind patterns in Houston-suggesting an air pollution effect-but are not consistently related to concurrent measures of concentration in air of several pollutants [CITATION_1] ."
